title: 1963 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 01)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1963 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This worked out pretty well the first time.  When I torrented that 50 year old 1964 music on Monday earlier this week, I wasn't sure if anyone would even be interested in downloading it for their collections.  But it did receive a lot of hits.  So, in keeping with that theme, here is a copy of all the 1963 Christian music in my collection.

My older music is limited, but I may scrape together a few more of these 50+ year old bundles.

In the mean while, there are 35 albums being shared today, including...
